@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_filvly(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.67 * v0)
    v1 = v1
    v1 = v0
    tmp = wp.abs((0.71 * v2))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.87) / (v1 + 0.75 + tmp + 0.35)))
    v1 = wp.exp(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
